  <Folder>
    <name>Leg 1 — Barcelona (May 17–18)</name>
    <open>1</open>
    <Placemark>
      <name>La Roca Village Outlet</name>
      <description>🛍️ BCN Leg 1 · May 17
Gucci, Prada, Loewe, Saint Laurent. Sign up for free Hands-Free Shopping membership on arrival.
Open 10AM–9PM · 40 min from city</description>
      <styleUrl>#style_bcn</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>2.33,41.614,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Vinitus Barcelona</name>
      <description>🍽️ BCN Leg 1 · May 17 · Dinner
Carrer del Consell de Cent 333 · ⭐4.4
Best tapas in Eixample — pintxos, anchovies, jamón croquetas, grilled octopus.
Book for 8 · vinitus.com · +34 934 53 47 48</description>
      <styleUrl>#style_bcn</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>2.163,41.391,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>Sagrada Família</name>
      <description>⛪ BCN Leg 1 · May 18 · 9AM
€26–36/person · Timed entry only — must book online.
Allow 2–2.5 hrs · sagradafamilia.org</description>
      <styleUrl>#style_bcn</styleUrl>
      <Point><coordinates>2.174,41.404,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
  </Folder>
